Dear @bodhielfman, You father our boys with more care, attention, love, playfulness, humor, energy, sensitivity and time invested than any other father I know. In turn, you are teaching & showing them how to be good fathers themselves, should that glorious moment happen for them in their own life. Thank you, thank you, thank you for being so present and devoted.  I can ALWAYS count on you as Dada. I love you. And, to my own Dad— I  MISS YOU.  I love you so much and miss our sweet chats, crossword puzzles, dancing together and snuggling on with the couch watching football.  I hope you feel this love burst surrounding you right now— wherever you might be.  I hope you are enjoying yourself. 💝 #HappyFathersDay #FathersDay I love all the men in my life.

The universe doing its thing! 🤘🏽👀🤘🏽

This hat, born from a spontaneous experiment, became a canvas for a new idea. Hand-dying the felt added that extra touch of uniquness.
I hadn’t played with dye before this, so I was excited to see how it would turn out.

While I was literally putting the finishing touches to this hat, I recieved a call from the lovely @therealkateceberano looking for a special gift for her dearest friend of 25+ years, @jennaelfman in town for just a brief visit. 
Timing would be tight to make something that quick, but the universe stepped in when I shared a photo of this hat in progress. Instantly, we knew it was the perfect creation.

These abstract hats aren’t for everyone, and that’s the point. They’re crafted for the ones meant to wear them. The universe works in mysterious ways, connecting us with the right person at the right time.

Such a joy to meet you, Jenna! Wishing you an incredible time in Australia. And sending heaps of love to you, Kate. 🫵🏼💜
Special mention to @adamsavillebrown for being in the right spot at the right time also. 🤘🏽
